This project combines components under different licenses. Each component
keeps its own license; the full texts are in the files referenced below.

1. Fonts — SIL Open Font License 1.1 (see LICENSE-OFL.txt)
   - files/Font.ttf
     Modified version of Google Sans Flex.
     Copyright 2015 Google LLC. All Rights Reserved.
   - files/GoogleSansVF.ttf
     Modified version of Google Sans (subset to its fallback role —
     Cyrillic, Greek, and supporting ranges; GRAD axis pinned).
     Copyright 2025 The Google Sans Project Authors
     (https://github.com/googlefonts/googlesans)
   - files/RobotoFB.ttf
     Modified version of Roboto (internally renamed to "RobotoFB";
     wdth axis pinned).
     Copyright 2011 The Roboto Project Authors
     (https://github.com/googlefonts/roboto-classic)
   The OFL requires the fonts, modified or unmodified, to remain under the
   OFL. They are bundled here with software of other licenses, which the OFL
   explicitly permits.

2. Installer scripts — GNU General Public License v2.0 (see LICENSE-GPL2.txt)
   - customize.sh, uninstall.sh, common/functions.sh, common/install.sh,
     META-INF/com/google/android/update-binary, updater-script
   Derived from the MMT-Extended module template,
   Copyright Zackptg5 (https://github.com/Zackptg5/MMT-Extended), GPL-2.0,
   by way of AndroSYNC's font module. Modifications for this module
   Copyright 2026 ethanm6, likewise under GPL-2.0.

3. Font configuration — Apache License 2.0 (see LICENSE-Apache2.txt)
   - files/fonts.xml, files/font_fallback.xml
   Derived from the Android Open Source Project / LineageOS system font
   configuration, Copyright The Android Open Source Project.

4. Font patch script — GNU General Public License v3.0 or later
